## User Input

```text
$ARGUMENTS
```

## Outline

1. Read `{{BRIEF_ARTIFACT}}`
2. Stop if `{{BRIEF_ARTIFACT}}` does not exist or is empty
3. Extract the slug from the `- Slug:` line in `{{BRIEF_ARTIFACT}}`
4. Stop if the extracted slug does not exactly match `$ARGUMENTS`
5. Do not brainstorm here; redirect to `{{BRIEF_ENTRYPOINT}}` if the brief is missing or incomplete
6. Run `/speckit.specify` using the approved brief as input
7. Run `/speckit.clarify` when critical ambiguity remains
8. Run `/speckit.plan`
9. If planning requires new technology outside the approved stack, STOP and request explicit approval
10. Run `/speckit.tasks`
11. Run `/speckit.analyze`
12. Run `/speckit.implement`
13. Run the blocking validation gates:
{{BLOCKING_GATES_INDENTED}}
14. Run the observational validation gates and record the outcome:
{{OBSERVATIONAL_GATES_INDENTED}}
15. Update `TEST_REPORT.md`
16. Update `REVIEW_REPORT.md`
17. Run a mandatory fix round
18. Re-run all validation gates
19. Generate `SNAPSHOT.md` last
